trans-unit.source: Represents a symbol binder for managed code.
trans-unit.target: 代表 managed 程式碼的符號繫結器。

trans-unit.source: **Note** ISymbolBinder1 is the managed counterpart of the unmanaged `ISymUnmanagedBinder` interface, one of the unmanaged symbol store interfaces that provide an alternative way to read and write debug symbol information.
trans-unit.target: **請注意**ISymbolBinder1 是的未受管理的 managed 對應項目`ISymUnmanagedBinder`介面提供的替代方法來讀取和寫入偵錯符號資訊的 unmanaged 的符號存放區介面之一。

trans-unit.source: Gets the interface of the symbol reader for the current file.
trans-unit.target: 目前檔案取得符號讀取器介面。

trans-unit.source: When given a pointer to a metadata interface, a file name, and a search path, the GetReader method returns the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.ISymbolReader> interface that reads the debugging symbols associated with the module.
trans-unit.target: 當指定指標的中繼資料介面、 為檔案名稱，並搜尋路徑，GetReader 方法會傳回<xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.ISymbolReader>讀取偵錯符號的模組相關聯的介面。</xref:System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.ISymbolReader>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.IntPtr> that refers to the metadata import interface.
The name of the file for which the reader interface is required.
trans-unit.target: 讀取器介面是必要的檔案名稱。

trans-unit.source: The search path used to locate the symbol file.
trans-unit.target: 用來尋找符號檔搜尋路徑。

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SymbolStore.ISymbolReader"></xref> interface that reads the debugging symbols.
